data.name: Creamy Avocado and Yogurt Dip
data.quickTastyDescription: A delightful, creamy dip that's perfect for snacking, made with fresh avocados and tangy yogurt.
detailedCookingInstructions: Scoop the flesh of the avocados into a mixing bowl.
Add the plain Greek yogurt and lime juice to the bowl.
Sprinkle in the garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.
Mash the ingredients together with a fork or a whisk until creamy and smooth.
If using, stir in the chopped fresh cilantro for added flavor.
Taste and adjust seasoning if necessary.
Serve immediately with fresh veggies, pita chips, or tortilla chips.
data.modifiersForBase: Using Greek yogurt for creaminess and tang
